(3) Everything that is nervous and shy and a rompus is a shumpus. (4) Everything that is discordant, melodic, and a brimpus is a yumpus. (5) Everything that is hot and cold and a rompus is a brimpus. (6) Stella is shy. (7) Stella is angry. (8) Stella is a rompus. (9) Stella is cold. (10) Stella is hot. (11) Stella is nervous. (12) Stella is a zumpus. (13) Stella is amenable.] Prove: (14) Stella is angry, amenable, and a brimpus.

根据前提我们可以得出以下信息：

(6) Stella is shy.
(7) Stella is angry.
(8) Stella is a rompus.
(9) Stella is cold.
(10) Stella is hot.
(11) Stella is nervous.
(12) Stella is a zumpus.

其中 (6)(7)(11) 可以得出 Stella 情绪变化比较大，经常生气和紧张。并且由于她是 rompus（假设），她很可能会害羞、谨慎且倾向于保持中立，这就解释了为什么她是 amenable 的（可容忍的）。而结合她的温度特征（cold and hot），可以推测出她的行为表现将会呈现出反常和反覆，即时而冷酷时而热情。因此，我们可以得出结论：Stella 是生气、可容忍的和害羞的。所以，根据以上前提和结论，我们可以得出：(14) Stella is angry, amenable, and a brimpus 是成立的。
